{
  "stem": "1061.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 1.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, we-- we had no idea that there was a Russian offensive from the East and there was going-- there was now a build up on the West-- in the West-- you know, that the Americans and the English were-- were trying to-- to bring an end to the war.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But we know-- we knew nothing of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We just knew that our suffering has now increased.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the rest of what was the bit of humanity that still remained with us in those-- in those camps in our hometown was now very much over.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I mean, that was now-- it wasn't a surreal world.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "This was hell.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, now this was living hell, and-- and this was something that we couldn't even comprehend.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I mean, we could comprehend being exhausted, and being hungry, and having lice, and working, and all.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "You know, and-- and-- and understanding the war effort, how they would squeeze the blood out of us for their war effort-- we could understand that, even I could.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But this place, Auschwitz, it was something incomprehensible.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I mean, we didn't really know the-- what the purpose of this place was, since we really never knew that this was a real killing camp-- that there were people coming in transport right into the-- into the crematories and into-- out the chimney.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We had no idea.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But this place didn't look like-- it had barbed wire that was electrified.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were taken into a barracks-- again, a lot of us from my hometown, you see?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were still in the group.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we were placed in the barracks, and we were on a type of a quarantine for about a month in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And what does quarantine mean?",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
